{"tid":567293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【懲罰選民】網民收到鄧家彪競選宣傳單張　郵票不足罰4蚊","createTime":"2018-02-20T17:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T17:30:24.000Z","uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"283750a6e84dabb02f19900278d2ced09ea6d97e","tid":567293,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180220/s00001/0627dcadeb25c4eb4f1de6b9ebf56571.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180220%2Fs00001%2F0627dcadeb25c4eb4f1de6b9ebf56571.jpg&h=77ea7a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會新界東補選下月11日舉行，各候選人近日宣傳攻勢不斷，擺街站、寄傳單等都係慣常手法。facebook群組「大埔」網友Bernardo Sin屋企，亦收到同時屬於工聯會同民建聯嘅鄧家彪競選宣傳單張，呼籲選民「全家總動員　齊投鄧家彪」。選民投票意向如何係後話，Bernardo關注嘅係，封信竟然無貼郵票，郵局話「郵費不足」，罰收件人4蚊！佢於是喺晚上發帖徵求其他人意見：「去郵局拎信前，可唔可以睇左係咩信先比（畀）罰款？」<br />\n<br />\n宣傳單張無貼郵票，搞到收件人受罰。雖然金額唔多，鄧家彪怕唔怕影響自己形象，進而對競選有影響？Emily嘗試搵鄧回覆。可能都夜喇，對方未應機。<br />\n<br />\n再提提大家，今屆新東補選候選人，除咗鄧家彪之外，仲有黃成智、陳玉娥、方國珊、趙佩玉同范國威。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180220/s00001/1519140358411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180220%2Fs00001%2F1519140358411&d=aNwrbK9P8ms9Qib0OXpBOmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=17f145fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180220%2Fs00001%2F1519140358411&h=48a00842\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180220/s00001/1519140358411</a>"},{"pid":"51d2cdd23222bed561e2cebbdc1f36eacf785ebf","tid":567293,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"「要攞住個兜嚟乞<del>票</del>郵資」<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20160905/s00046/a076986faef252865bb4631c9a7b1da2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20160905%2Fs00046%2Fa076986faef252865bb4631c9a7b1da2.jpg&h=195164ba&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}